title: [CRASH] Redis seems to be crashing while creating RDB.
body:
[CrashResport.txt](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/17022341/CrashResport.txt)
Redis server is trying to write to RDB where  the  for object hash o->encoding  is neither  OBJ_ENCODING_LISTPACK  nor OBJ_ENCODING_HT  Hence it enters server panic. From there its crashing during memory test. Server was able to restart only after a successful memorytest.
